[@slide] What the partnership puts in one place
[@subtitle] GlobalFreight Connect · 120,000 traders · 42 countries
[@note] The product story in four tiles. The point of the callout: a single workflow, not four logins. [/@note]

[cards cols:2]
  [card icon:truck title:"Freight payments"] Pay carriers as shipments move. [/card]
  [card icon:banknotes title:"Supplier settlements"] Settle suppliers across borders. [/card]
  [card icon:document-currency-euro title:"Customs fees"] Clear duties without leaving the lane. [/card]
  [card icon:document-text title:"Invoices"] Issue and reconcile in the same view. [/card]
[/cards]

[callout tone:key icon:puzzle-piece] One platform, one workflow — embedded where the work already happens. [/callout]

